个事情我就不方便再介入了。” 记者就此事致电爱奇艺剧集《漂白》总制片人马女士，其表示“首先我们的剧集是买自一本由作家出版社出版的，由陈枰编写的小说《漂白》，我们有小说完整的版权链。但是我们目前也在积极处理和沟通这件事，跟各个团队对比，完整的事件信息可以等官方说明，其他的事情我个人不方便做出回应。”随后，新黄河记者在网上搜索发现，确实有一本由作家出版社出版的、陈枰编写的小说《漂白》。电视剧《漂白》编剧回应抄袭争议"},"attached_info":"CkEIh5CCnZ3YtrlxEAMaCTExMzAwODg2MCDNpLy8BjAAODFABXILMTAxNjQyNjc3ODV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"140 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-1b464091c7003a188a21e5aaf40249f9_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1737520243.739898","card_id":"Q_10209196035","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":10209196035,"title":"如何评价2025年1月《王者荣耀世界》获得版号？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/10209196035","type":"question","created":1737465849,"answer_count":23,"follower_count":29,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[253,163534,186183,1512647],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"会是什么类型的玩法？会对已有的开放世界游戏造成什么影响？"},"attached_info":"CkEIh5CCnZ3YtrlxEAMaCTExMzAxNzkwNyD5v768BjAAOB1ABnILMTAyMDkxOTYwMzV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"91 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-489cb754f08cddb5f837794305828c4b_1440w.png?source=7e7ef6e2&needBackground=1"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1737520243.740149","card_id":"Q_4238823948","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":4238823948,"title":"果郡王为什么因为听到一句「逆风如解意，容易莫摧残」就对甄嬛念念不忘？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/4238823948","type":"question","created":17